{"tid":2387743,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得班mk連登仔先會睇唔起鍾意追idol既人","createTime":"2021-01-30T14:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T12:32:25.000Z","uid":4618,"like":18,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8321c47f024d81abc3c5b0e5ebca6d3116080042","tid":2387743,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsRUKr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsRUKr6.jpg&h=6229a46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多現充mk都對追idol呢樣興趣有好多誤會，以為追idol就等於毒、猥褻、膽小內向、不善交際，會戴住有色眼鏡歧視，對佢地好唔友善。<br />\n<br />\n老實講呢種諗法都已經過時咗十年，已經2021仲停留喺封建思想，唔識跟隨時代進步，以為自己睇唔起人，其實係自己自卑感作崇。<br />\n<br />\n我講幾個例子俾大家聽，就知追idol既人根本唔係班mk想像到咁，釐清誤解之餘，順便開闊下大家眼界。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球首富、備受大家推崇既Elon Musk，早排都唔怕羞恥咁公開自己推、更加暗示睇idol係佢努力工作既原動力<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1349129669258448897?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1349129669258448897%3Fs%3D21&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=a36d2cd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1349129669258448897%3Fs%3D21&h=7d057ec0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1349129669258448897?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n今年日本文壇最高殿堂芥川賞，得獎既《推し、燃ゆ》正正係一位少女追idol跌跌撞撞既心路歷程<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XYbYrVw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXYbYrVw.jpg&h=5d08b80c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉呢兩個例子唔係想表達咩，無論係有財有勢既社會賢達，定係追求極緻藝術既純文學創作，都不但只冇貶低追idol呢個行為，更加係加以肯定，就連自己都係追idol既一員。<br />\n<br />\n眼見動物台仲喺度討論緊天竺鼠車車點解紅、鬼滅係咪細蚊仔睇、巨人係咪神作、鋼鍊係咪哲學，老實講根本無所謂，如果你仲晒時間執著呢啲論題要拗贏人，就證明你自己仲係呢種層次。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家唔想停留喺呢個階段，想要改變自己，我希望你地會補返上年年度最佳動畫《虹咲學園學園偶像同好會》，踏出自己舒適圈既一步，一定可以望到更廣闊既新天空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWLRM4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiWLRM4d.jpg&h=5a4fd883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6rYT31OEFvk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6rYT31OEFvk&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=ba35927e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6rYT31OEFvk</a>"},{"pid":"07b1899d9860a969b4abd1067d0eb3664cf3e87f","tid":2387743,"uid":197836,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"追idol 既人都唔會係壞人"},{"pid":"c715b8d8ed961799c82f687232959e316abcad9d","tid":2387743,"uid":4618,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07b1899d9860a969b4abd1067d0eb3664cf3e87f","tid":2387743,"uid":197836,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"追idol 既人都唔會係壞人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"拉康講過追idol係超越自我既最高層次"},{"pid":"54b24a82975f8343a64aa84ad125347e5ed8b61b","tid":2387743,"uid":197836,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c715b8d8ed961799c82f687232959e316abcad9d","tid":2387743,"uid":4618,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07b1899d9860a969b4abd1067d0eb3664cf3e87f","tid":2387743,"uid":197836,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"追idol 既人都唔會係壞人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"拉康講過追idol係超越自我既最高層次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"邊q個係拉康&hellip;"},{"pid":"dcfece358c745501b6d2ee565730b66828e7baba","tid":2387743,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"我日日都著住樋口圓香既T返工"},{"pid":"6cd6770b153415551d0a7a3800eb4ccf269d6888","tid":2387743,"uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"54b24a82975f8343a64aa84ad125347e5ed8b61b","tid":2387743,"uid":197836,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c715b8d8ed961799c82f687232959e316abcad9d","tid":2387743,"uid":4618,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07b1899d9860a969b4abd1067d0eb3